thread.title: Janet O'Reilly
thread.title_full: Temple & Webster reviewed by Janet O'Reilly

author: Janet O'Reilly
title: Janet O'Reilly
text: Bed came within time frame suggested, pretty easy to put together but one of the legs didn't fit into the screw. I emailed right away and was asked to send pictures which I did. I was offered a replacement but as the bed was already built and I have visitors arriving I declined so I was offered a discount which I accepted. Very quick and understanding customer service.
